com.xilinx.rapidwright.design

Class PartitionPin

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.PartitionPin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PartitionPin
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a routing interface point that can be attached to a logical port or pin of a cell. A partition pin is mapped to a specific node (described by its base wire) in the fabric.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
